snippet.textDisplay:
People keep using the "Demacia can just kill their citizens for casting magic, good or bad" to make Noxia look better.
Again, THE WORLD ISN'T JUST BLACK AND WHITE (THEY NEVER SAID DEMACIA IS GOOD AND NOXIA IS BAD)!! There are differents between merciful and justice!!!
"They using the word 'justice' for the murder they cause". Justice is about law and order, not second chances like many of you thought.
How many of you don't even know the reason why Demacia hate magic and just believe in whatever rumors they said the most? They're afraid of it from the beginning.
There are always good and bad, but you can't blame them on something they're afraid. Demacia is known for justice (WHICH IS EXACTLY WHY THEY'RE SO STRICT IN LAWS, or else, they'll already be fallen from the evasion). They take away many child from their family just because they have magic but again, they didn't do it for nasty experiments and stuff, they have fear. But atleast they're also have honor and loyalty (while Noxia sometime betrayed their own people, Riven and Urgot). And some individuals that are so badly want to serve their country (Garen).
Lux is trying to change their mind about magic, that they can be used for good, but you can't just convince a crowd that what they fear isn't true.
Overall, Demacia is still better than Noxia in many ways (again, I'm not saying that Noxia is bad, they respect power but the "at any cost" way creep me).
Demacia is many thing and y'all judging it just because of one really show what you are.
